{
  "stem": "19198.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We didn't know what was on the tray, except that the-- as-- as he came through the door, Dr.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Gluek mentioned to his mother-in-law, in whose home we really were meeting, and she sent the butler back out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It took a little while before butler came back with five platters of scrambled eggs.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "What we found out later was the reason for Dr.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Gluek sending the first load back to the kitchen is that they was serving the eggs with bacon.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So since we did not know that at that time, this was one introduction to American Reformed Judaism that we almost got.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It-- we were impressed by the size of the school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I've got to tell you the Hebrew Union College in Cincinnati, which was built in its present-- or in its then shape-- in the early 1900's, except for its library, which was more recent, was a-- an extensive campus with three or four imposing buildings, far beyond anything that we had seen owned by any Jewish organization in Germany.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that by itself impressed us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The-- the dormitory, where each of us had his own room, again was something that was most impressive to us, because we were not aware of any facility of that sort, even in a secular school in Germany.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The-- as soon as-- after breakfast we arrived at the school, we-- we-- we were welcomed by a number of-- of students.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The school year hadn't started yet, so the-- the whole student body wasn't there yet.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And every one of the students did his best-- and I can say his, because there were no-- no girl students at that time-- they did his best to make us feel welcome and at home.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
